net.sf.sprockets.google

Class StreetView.Params

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.sprockets.google.StreetView.Params
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    StreetViewParams
    Enclosing class:
    StreetView

    @Value.Modifiable
public abstract static class StreetView.Params
extends Object

    Parameters for the Google Street View Image API service. Example usage: 

    Params.create().location("empire state bldg")
         .pitch(30).fov(100).width(360).height(480);
